Text:
sjbrand, you sir (or madam!), are simply fabulous!

i was a little scepticle when i first saw this, but i've got to say, you deliver what you promise. literally EVERYTHING! all the classics as well as some wickid unheard mixes!

everything is accurately and painstakingly labelled too. 

super fast DL time too!

again, your a star

looking forward to getting my hands on the rest of you discogs, and of course, will seed forever!
